{"tid":500290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好眼淺","createTime":"2017-12-15T15:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:51:39.000Z","uid":20061,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6b02c45583a16845edf4559795c1e24e16c42a1e","tid":500290,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣<br />\n唔係講緊同人嗌交好易喊<br />\n係好容易代入一套電視劇一個mv生死分離既情節，特別覺得自己承受唔到身邊愛既人有一日離開自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如話見到老豆多左好多白頭髮個樣殘左；諗起遲下可能半年去外國飛前同男朋友係離境大堂個到暫別；成日諗起身邊既人去世前同自己講既說話... 我都會自己偷偷地喊<br />\n其實我都覺得自己好痴線諗得好極端，但明明平日既我好樂觀，我仲覺得自己人生係愉快知足的，仲會成日安慰輔導朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能自己經歷得唔夠多，又覺得自己已經擁有好多，好怕會突然失去擁有既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點樣可以制止下自己，成日眼腫腫唔係辦法"},{"pid":"2a341ffd143b958b5470ccec62503cd5a8bb160e","tid":500290,"uid":431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"諗諗下衰嘢就會喊<br />\n睇返舊對話紀錄又會好似經歷多一次咁又喊<br />\n又少少嘢就感動鼻酸好想喊<br />\n上youtube見到靚景嗰啲片都會流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇agt嗰啲會想像埋人哋點努力之後表演得好成功有人欣賞之後為人喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd1cd50bfe917825a944303a8c46e88d378fd81","tid":500290,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"嗚嗚嗚"},{"pid":"55d0d66b625121985d2610e7ba6fea03f7a0559b","tid":500290,"uid":1274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"會！<br />\n睇到運動員奮力奔跑時都會喊出來，<br />\n睇見好多不公義嘅事會喊，<br />\n睇戲更加，<br />\n唔關自己事嘅，都可以流眼淚"},{"pid":"730f5adb19465661e48962d01c53d4c4bb3dade7","tid":500290,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:52:53.000Z","msg":"一激動好嬲好忟又喊"},{"pid":"7b58df0358f7413573018f7bf100672efb21c6fb","tid":500290,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"受委屈又喊"},{"pid":"ee8d12fb0381d15199c4c13e3d7447eb2ced7471","tid":500290,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"開心又喊"},{"pid":"74a4747d4d01fda684b0914bf4060555b088ea07","tid":500290,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"又唔係成日嘅 我應該唔算眼淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇劇嘅話通常係見到啲好人俾人屈嘅情節就會想喊<br />\n有時會望住阿媽 睇到佢呢幾年老左咁多身體差咗咁多 就會好驚佢有一日會離開我 跟住就會想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d078530c3e68663f0a24f58271830651ad153a6e","tid":500290,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1b78ea526ee2eb4957edc45b00a20364e3a8f58","tid":500290,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻眼好深，好似渣左眼影咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49f8d64361730f618f287849bbe65a09a0f42af","tid":500290,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗諗下衰嘢就會喊<br />\n睇返舊對話紀錄又會好似經歷多一次咁又喊<br />\n又少少嘢就感動鼻酸好想喊<br />\n上youtube見到靚景嗰啲片都會流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇agt嗰啲會想像埋人哋點努力之後表演得好成功有人欣賞之後為人喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解睇到靚景會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db8ba4f1630e12dad901b7112d71aace2e12717","tid":500290,"uid":13032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"諗下同女朋友分手就會想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67161e3863235d8bc86bcb7d64d396b91534ec49","tid":500290,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"朋友仔一句問候都會搞到我眼濕濕"},{"pid":"e070f692f2a8f7133696157485acf92af4483dc8","tid":500290,"uid":159400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"眼淺姐係比較感性 情緒易被牽動<br />\n感情豐富既人好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得呢個係優點"},{"pid":"dc2a315cdcaf1cbd77d85246f86d3f0c6adbe9d4","tid":500290,"uid":24642,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"幼稚園已經畀老師評我做大喊包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係好堅強<br />\n人哋一語氣重少少<br />\n我就開始嚟料<br />\n受少少委屈   一同人講又會<br />\n一講中我要害又會<br />\n好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇戲又係<br />\n只要有少少少感動位就會想流馬尿<br />\n又要忍住忍住唔喊 chok住chok住搞到喉嚨痛咁<br />\n<br />\n有時覺得自己好煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明自己感受應該唔係好深<br />\n但唔知點解出嚟嘅反應一定會大到要喊咁"},{"pid":"2da86e5c44ba10209abc1a38c77354d27f04178c","tid":500290,"uid":84478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗諗下衰嘢就會喊<br />\n睇返舊對話紀錄又會好似經歷多一次咁又喊<br />\n又少少嘢就感動鼻酸好想喊<br />\n上youtube見到靚景嗰啲片都會流淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇agt嗰啲會想像埋人哋點努力之後表演得好成功有人欣賞之後為人喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望到好靚嘅景會喊 睇煙花覺得好浪漫又喊"},{"pid":"963d6645cf3b9943927f0c22329008996e85bd81","tid":500290,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"見到人喊自己都想喊"},{"pid":"33da4f031d63bc0810045bf405678808dc2314d0","tid":500290,"uid":141496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09393bdf41c6a8c8e392783a167787cb1127f317","tid":500290,"uid":139049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"極度容易喊...睇多啦A 夢大電影都喊得出...<br />\n同fd鬧交又喊 諗返個ex又喊 睇電視見到啲人講遺言都會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d3174638e28c7e755ca295581fca4192028373","tid":500290,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"關我撚事 生活好過d"},{"pid":"fcb34cd14fb25c312df9203214c5b88132ae7ec9","tid":500290,"uid":155062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"唱生日歌都會感動到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23195a5880d83f425d04b031c8870186ec69f4bd","tid":500290,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:12:21.000Z","msg":"好怕失去<br />\n<br />\n我係男都眼淺到成個女人咁"},{"pid":"39f14284f12d31fb3b843df947b243cc189ca4fa","tid":500290,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事 生活好過d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2f159532bf9d7a4076f489e3f02e457e52abac","tid":500290,"uid":161359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"女朋友就係甘 喊濕我幾件衫"},{"pid":"8ebd10181722531111eeed232632b4883ce16478","tid":500290,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"睇埋留言<br />\n好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}